  "title": "ASSISTANT ENGINEER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong><br />The role involves detailed engineering design, site coordination, and supervision of BMS installation, testing, and commissioning works. The candidate will also provide technical support to ensure seamless integration of BMS with ACMV, electrical, and other M&E systems.<br /><br /><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>· Carry out detailed engineering design, system configurations, and shop drawing preparation for BMS works.</p><p>· Supervise and coordinate BMS installation, wiring, and system integration on site.</p><p>· Conduct testing, commissioning, troubleshooting, and fine-tuning of BMS systems.</p><p>· Ensure all BMS works comply with project specifications, design standards, and statutory requirements.</p><p>· Liaise with consultants, subcontractors, and internal teams to resolve technical issues.</p><p>· Prepare technical documentation, progress reports, and operation manuals.<br /></p><p></p>",
